info.name: Route Mobile Email API Documentation
info.description:
Welcome to the Route Mobile developer hub. You'll find comprehensive Email API documentation to help you start working with Route Mobile as quickly as possible, as well as support if you get stuck. Let's jump right in!

Contact Support:
 Name: Route Mobile Development

query.description: (Required) The ID of the owner or sender of the email.
(Required) A security token or authentication token that authorizes the API request.

(Required) The ID of the email template to be used for composing the email content.

(Required) The email address from which the email will be sent.
(Required)  The recipient's email address.
